text: ai mere paalane vaale jis baat kee ye aurate mujh se khvaahish rakhatee hain usakee nisvat (badale mein) mujhe qaid khaanon jyaada pasand hai aur agar too in auraton ke fareb mujhase dapha na pharamaega to (shaayad) mai unakee taraph mael (jhuk) ho jaanoo le to jao aur jaahilon se shumaar kiya jaoon
